data.description:
Great first time buyer home located just minutes from Alvords highly rated School District. This home boasts New flooring, New roof, New ac system, New insulation in the attic, New cabinets and countertops, an Oversized laundry area, and a closet with built ins. 
Huge yard on corner lot. You can see the elementary school from the house. Newly ground electrical in the laundry room, kitchen and bathrooms, New water heater, Lots of natural lighting, Covered porch, 2 car carport, Newly graveled driveway.
